public class ResumeButton
extends Abutton

Author:
zacharymailloux The class ResumeButton was originally intended to be used as my example of inheritance. However, upon adding more complex things that I wanted my button to do it quickly became clear that having all three buttons properly work would be beyond my level of understanding what exactly is shared with other classes.
